data.description: Almost 3000 ft.2 in this 4 bed, 2.5 bath in popular Wellington NE neighborhood! Tons of space on the main level make it great for entertaining. Living room, family room with fireplace, huge great room with cathedral ceilings, all rolling out to a custom patio. Formal dining room, beautifully updated kitchen with center island, and bedrooms are all generous in size. Home sits on a private lot on a quiet cul-de-sac. Recently landscaped and home is available for a quick possession. Neighborhood pool just a short walking distance away! Just minutes from downtown Noblesville.
